description: The exhibition hall of King Sejong Memorial Hall is built on the ground floor of the square. The memorial hall is dedicated to introducing the "story" of King Sejong the Great and the main events of his life. The various models displayed in the museum are covered with Korean characters and some Chinese characters, describing the achievements of King Sejong.

address: 12 Samil-daero 30-gil, Nakwon-dong, Jongno-gu, Seoul, South Korea
684 Tongil-ro, Nokbeon-dong, Eunpyeong-gu, Seoul, South Korea
